ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T18:10:12.000Z","msg":"國民黨除左老屈對手，根本無料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}